OL,7,FScotland's fire and rescue service is
OL,8,Fin the grip of a bullying "crisis"
OL,9,Fwith more than one in five employees
OL,10,Fhaving been victim of or witnessed
OL,11,Finappropriate behaviour.
OL,13,FAn ITV Border investigation has
OL,14,Funcovered a series of concerns around
OL,15,Fdiscrimination and harassment which
OL,16,Fhas worsened in recent years.
OL,26,@pD@[OUpD@bO]
