OL,7,FLynn Sweeney, 65, worked for the
OL,8,Fservice for 18 years and last year had
OL,9,Fa grievance upheld after she
OL,10,Fcomplained about bullying by two
OL,11,Fmanagers.
OL,13,FShe said that they spoke
OL,14,Finappropriately towards staff members,
OL,15,Fwhich culminated in them acting in an
OL,16,F"extremely aggressive" manner towards
OL,17,Fher during a disagreement at a fire
OL,18,Fstation in Clydebank.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@VO]
