OL,7,FShe was signed off work after the
OL,8,Flatter incident and did not return but
OL,9,Fsaid she was repeatedly pressured by
OL,10,Fsenior management to return and to
OL,11,Fdrop the complaint.
OL,13,F"At the end of the day, I loved my
OL,14,Fjob," she said. "But I hated the
OL,15,Fculture. And that's something that you
OL,16,Fcan't control."
OL,26,@uD@AOUvD@EO]vD@QOUxD@OO]
