OL,7,FITV News has spoken to three other
OL,8,Fstaff members, including a former
OL,9,Fsenior officer, a current employee and
OL,10,Fa former staff member. Each
OL,11,Fhighlighted what they called a "toxic"
OL,12,Fculture within the service.
OL,14,FThe former firefighter said: "Bullying
OL,15,Fand harassment, combined with immoral
OL,16,Fand unethical behaviours has become
OL,17,Fcommonplace, particularly at a senior
OL,18,Flevel. Anyone who tries to challenge
OL,19,Fthis behaviour or raise complaints,
OL,20,Fincluding those in senior positions,
OL,21,Fare subtly sidelined and marginalised."
OL,26,@sD@`OUsD@fO]vD@^OU}D@gO]
