OL,7,FThe current staff member said:
OL,8,F"Management comes together to protect
OL,9,Fthemselves at all costs, but ordinary
OL,10,Fworkers are continually thrown under
OL,11,Fthe bus."
OL,13,FThe former employee said they were
OL,14,Fleft unable to sleep because of
OL,15,F"bullying and bad management", adding:
OL,16,F"It is a dangerously toxic culture."
