OL,7,FSimilar concerns were highlighted by
OL,8,Fsenior officials in the Fire Brigades
OL,9,FUnion, who said a "boys' club" exists
OL,10,Fwithin the service that has failed to
OL,11,Fdeal with serious problems.
OL,13,FThis anecdotal evidence is backed up
OL,14,Fby internal staff surveys, which have
OL,15,Fbeen obtained using freedom of
OL,16,Finformation legislation.
