OL,7,FInternal research carried out last
OL,8,Fyear found that 21 per cent of
OL,9,Femployees who replied "have personally
OL,10,Fexperienced or observed
OL,11,Fdiscrimination, bullying and/or
OL,12,Fharassment in the workplace over the
OL,13,Flast 12 months".
OL,15,FOf those who said they had seen or
OL,16,Fbeen victim of bullying, harassment or
OL,17,Fdiscrimination, fewer than half (45
OL,18,Fper cent) reported the behaviour
OL,19,Finternally.
OL,26,@qD@WOUuD@OO]
