OL,7,FJust 17 per cent of people who
OL,8,Fescalated concerns were satisfied with
OL,9,Fthe outcome. The remaining 83 per cent
OL,10,Fsaid they were unhappy with the
OL,11,Fresults.
OL,13,FThe only other staff survey undertaken
OL,14,Fby the service, which took place in
OL,15,F2018, found that 10 per cent of staff
OL,16,Fmembers said they had "personally
OL,17,Fexperienced bullying or harassment at
OL,18,Fwork".
