OL,7,FMrs Sweeney said there was an
OL,8,F"embedded" cultural problem in the
OL,9,FScottish Fire and Rescue Service,
OL,10,Fadding: "But it's a case of, 'We are
OL,11,Fhere to protect the organisation, not
OL,12,Fthe individual'."
OL,14,FA separate investigation took place
OL,15,Finto the two individuals involved but
OL,16,Fthe service said it was unable to
OL,17,Fdisclose the outcome of that because
OL,18,Fof confidentiality requirements.
