OL,7,FHowever, in a letter to Mrs Sweeney,
OL,8,Fseen by ITV News, a senior officer
OL,9,Fsaid: "I can advise the appropriate
OL,10,Factions were taken."
OL,12,FMrs Sweeny's doctor said she was
OL,13,Funable to go back to her job because
OL,14,Fof the impact of the process on her
OL,15,Fmental health.
OL,17,FBut her application to retire on ill-
OL,18,Fhealth grounds was rejected and she
OL,19,Fwas dismissed because she could not go
OL,20,Fback to work after a near two-year
OL,21,Fabsence.
