OL,7,FShe said: "This didn't just affect my
OL,8,Fjob. It impacted on who I was as a
OL,9,Fperson. And I didn't want to become
OL,10,Fthe person that I was becoming. I was
OL,11,Falways the strong one, the one that
OL,12,Fspoke up. I was always the go to
OL,13,Fperson at home and outwith.
OL,15,F"And suddenly I was at the point where
OL,16,FI didn't want to drive, where my
OL,17,Fhusband became a taxi driver. I didn't
OL,18,Fwant to go places where there were too
OL,19,Fmany people or people I didn't know.
OL,20,FAnd I just wanted me back."
