OL,7,FIn 2022, Martin Blunden quit as chief
OL,8,Fofficer while an investigation was
OL,9,Fongoing into bullying allegations. The
OL,10,Fservice said at the time that it could
OL,11,Fnot comment on the probe into the
OL,12,Fclaims. He was replaced by Ross
OL,13,FHaggart, who retired after just a year
OL,14,Fin post.
OL,16,FOpposition parties called for an
OL,17,Finvestigation to take place into the
OL,18,Fculture in the service.
