OL,7,FTwo years ago, Scottish Conservative
OL,8,Fleader Russell Findlay raised what he
OL,9,Fcalled "detailed concerns about an
OL,10,Falleged culture of bullying, cronyism
OL,11,Fand poor governance relating to
OL,12,FScotland's national fire service, but
OL,13,Fthese were dismissed by SNP ministers".
OL,15,FHe said: "It was clear back then that
OL,16,Fthere were serious problems, but the
OL,17,Fgovernment showed no interest in doing
OL,18,Fthe right thing.
OL,26,@qD@HOUuD@fO]wD@JOU
