OL,7,F"They must now show respect for
OL,8,Ffirefighters by listening to them,
OL,9,Fproperly investigating these fresh
OL,10,Fallegations and taking the appropriate
OL,11,Faction."
OL,13,FScottish Labour's community safety
OL,14,Fspokesperson Katy Clark said: "These
OL,15,Fshocking reports suggest there is a
OL,16,Fbullying crisis unfolding in the
OL,17,FScottish Fire and Rescue Service.
