OL,7,FMr Stevens said: "One of my top
OL,8,Fpriorities is to improve the culture
OL,9,Fand leadership within the service and
OL,10,Fwe are committed to creating a
OL,11,Fworkplace where all staff are treated
OL,12,Fwith dignity and respect.
OL,14,F"Getting this right is a priority. We
OL,15,Fhave developed an action plan with
OL,16,Fcolleagues and trade union
OL,17,Frepresentatives and considered sector-
OL,18,Fwide lessons learned."
